flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 66: YouTube Shopping and Live Product Overlay Integration Flow

  Setup[Vendor selects products for live/video]
  Map[Map PRISM product IDs to YouTube shopping items]
  MappingOK{All mappings valid?}

  Publish[Publish shoppable overlays]
  Viewers[Viewers click product overlay]
  Route[Route click to PRISM product/cart flow]
  Track[Record source attribution and conversion events]

  Suppress[Suppress invalid overlays]
  Repair[Prompt vendor to repair mapping]
  Fallback[Fallback destination to vendor storefront]

  Setup --> Map --> MappingOK
  MappingOK -- Yes --> Publish --> Viewers --> Route --> Track
  MappingOK -- No --> Suppress --> Repair --> Map

  Route -->|Link integrity failed| Fallback --> Track
